value.0: I am the Archdruid Aawill and you are <FullName>. You are seeking hair from a dryad to save your city. Perhaps we can help each other.
The wind stole your name and intention from your lips and carried it to the trees, who whispered it to me.

This is not a responsibility to be taken on lightly... I dare not send someone who is only partially committed. Save the woods, and I shall give you the location of a dryad that you need to save your city.
I find your attitude lacking and unappreciative of the importance of this mission. Regardless, we both have things that we must do.
On another note, we had sent some druids on a mission to also restore the Spirit of the Woods, but they have not returned. Speak with the others in this camp for more information.
You can find it in the heart, or center of Neverwinter Wood. There is a ancient ritual you must perform there: first, find a stone altar within a hidden grove.
I have given you a special dagger forged from the woods itself. Use it to spill some of your blood on the altar. That will transport you to the realm where the Spirit of the Wood is.
I wish you luck.
Nature protect you.

Something is wrong with the Spirit of the Wood. I need you to investigate and cure it, so the forest can return to it's natural state. In return, I shall give you the location of a dryad that you need for your quest.
As promised, I will tell you the location of the dryad. You will find the fey deep inside the heart of the forest. I have already communicated with her and she will no longer hide from you.
I cannot promise you that she will give up her hair just like that, however. But before that, please allow me to give you this magical stone.
It is blessed by the Spirit of the Wood to have the power of healing once per day. Best of luck to you in your journeys.
Nope. That's not my name. And you are mistaken.
What did you need help with?
I think I can handle that, if you can tell me where I can find a dryad.
Where can I find the Spirit of the Wood?
I will be on my way.
Can you give me a buff?
Where can I find the Spirit of the Wood?
Farewell.
Can you take me to the dryad?
Can you take me to the dryad again?
